of the firms common stock, at an exercise price of
$42.42 per share, subject to certain antidilution
and other adjustments. the seriesk preferred stock
qualifies as tier 1 capital.
the seriesk preferred stock bears cumulative
dividends at a rate of 5% per year for the first
five years and 9% per year thereafter. the seriesk preferred
stock ranks equally with the firms existing 6.15%
cumulative preferred stock, seriese;
